1. *Roditelje* smo učili osnovne vrednosti. (We taught our parents basic values.)
2. Oni su imali puno razumevanja kada su im *roditelji* ispričali svoju priču. (They had a lot of understanding when their parents told them their story.)
3. Kada sam bio mali, *roditelji* su me učili da budem obazriv. (When I was little, my parents taught me to be careful.)
4. *Roditelji* su nam dali najbolje što su mogli. (Our parents gave us the best they could.)
5. Oni su uvek brinuli o svojoj deci, pa su se trudili da im *roditelji* omoguće sve najbolje. (They always cared for their children, so they tried to provide their parents with the best.)